node.text: Ah Ngor is a dashing beauty in a different era . I always sigh to her fate .  Tonight she is extremely beautiful in short tight cheongsam , perfect Huadan with natural Phoenix eyes .  Very eyes catching in pretty lotus - sleeved faint egg yolk coloured dress .  About to fall prey to her evil 师伯
She is seldom featured but I always think she is the lotus in the show.
